Another update to make your photos trendy as never before!
 
We’ve simplified a photo selection process. Now find images for editing easier and faster: from your photostream, among portrait photos, recently used pics and, of course, samples.

Get a bunch of new amazing effects: to find new arrivals open the ‘Effects’ tab and pay attention to green numbers next to the group names. For example, +4 next to ‘Face Montages’ means that we’ve added four new templates there.

Explore recently added ‘Smart filters’ category with its stylish and modern-looking filters.

And don't forget to share your creations, the world should see its heroes!

This update will definitely make your week brighter!

Summer is around the corner, so check out new exotic and tropical templates. Get stunning results with our new filters, double exposures and art effects.

We’ve added more awesome ways to make the post processing even more exciting. Combine several effects in almost no time to create true artworks. 

Finally, this version's bug fixes will prevent the app from crushes.

May the creativity be with you!

And if you want a dreamy-looking selfie among flowers, head to 'Double Exposures'.
